rComments: best professor i've ever had. I would love to have him again. if he has grandkids, I envy them so much. He is the best ever!!!!!!!!!
Very nice guy overall. Very enthusiastic and interesting lectures. Guy is full of energy jumping around everywhere during lecture. Only complaint is that his lectures are too short.

He's a really nice guy and is willing to take time clarifying concepts with you.  He is quite dull, repetitive and can quickly get off track/forget what he was talking about during a class. He still is incredibly knowledgeable.
Prof is very nice, material is interesting. However, don't take this course if you want a good grade. even you get A+ for the midterm and assignments, you will fail the final.
The final is definitely a killer but I think he has to do that because the midterm and assignments are sososo easy. He is a really nice prof and he explains the concept very clear.

He absolutely SCREWED us on the final. If you look at the anti-calendar you'll probably find relatively OK ratings. That was before the final. He MURDERED us. If you want to be mislead for an entire semester and then taken out to pasture and shot... His class is the one.
